member.example:
In the following example User entity has three associations of different types.

            public class User : Entity
            {
              ...

              // One-to-one association with "User" propery of "Account" class.
              [Association(PairTo = "User")]
              public Account Account { get; private set; }

              // One-to-many association
              [Association(PairTo = "Author")]
              public EntitySet<BlogPost> BlogPostss { get; private set; }

              // Many-to-many association
              [Association(PairTo = "Friends")]
              public EntitySet<User> Friends { get; private set; }
            }

